quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  50,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  50,1,Qaaf (arabic Alphabet ) quran Majeed ki qasam ( ke Mohammad paighambar khuda hain )
  50,2,lekin un logon ne taajjubkiya ke unhi mein se aik hadaayat karne wala un ke paas aaya to kafir kehnay lagey ke yeh baat to ( barri ) ajeeb hai
  50,3,bhala jab hum mar gay aur matti hogaye ( to phir zindah hon ge? ) yeh zindah hona ( aqal se ) baeed hai
  50,4,un ke jismon ko zameen jitna ( kha kha kar ) kam karti jati hai hamein maloom hai. aur hamaray paas tehreeri yad dasht bhi hai
  50,5,balkay ( ajeeb baat yeh hai ke ) jab un ke paas ( deen ) haq aa pouncha to unhon ne is ko jhoot samgha so yeh aik uljhi hui baat mein ( par rahay ) hain
  50,6,kiya unhon ne apne oopar aasman ki taraf nigah nahi ki ke hum ne is ko kyonkr banaya aur ( kyonkr ) sajaya aur is mein kahin shagaaf taq nahi
  50,7,aur zameen ko ( dekho usay ) hum ne phelaya aur is mein pahar rakh diye aur is mein har terhan ki khushnuma cheeze agayiN
  50,8,taakay rujoo laane walay bande hadaayat aur nasiyaat haasil karen
  50,9,aur aasman se barket wala pani utaara aur is se baagh o bastaan ugaye aur khaiti ka anaaj
  50,10,aur lambi lambi khjorin jin ka گابھا teh bah teh hota hai
  50,11,( yeh sab kuch ) bundon ko rozi dainay ke liye (kiya hai ) aur is ( pani ) se hum ne shehar murda ( yani zameen aftada ) ko zindahkiya. ( bas ) isi terhan ( qayamat ke roz ) nikal parna hai
  50,12,un se pehlay Nooh ki qoum aur kunwein walay aur smod jhutla chuke hain
  50,13,aur Aad aur firaon aur Loot ke bhai
  50,14,aur ban ke rehne walay aur tba ki qoum. ( gharz ) un sab ne payghambaroon ko jhtlaya to hamara vayd ( azaab ) bhi poora ho kar raha
  50,15,kiya hum pehli baar peda karkay thak gay hain? ( nahi ) balkay yeh az sar e no peda karne mein shak mein ( parre hue ) hain
  50,16,aur hum hi ne ensaan ko pedakiya hai aur jo khayalat is ke dil mein guzarte hain hum un ko jantay hain. aur hum is ki rug jaan se bhi is se ziyada qareeb hain
  50,17,"jab ( woh koi kaam karta hai to ) do likhnay walay jo dayen baen baithy hain, likh letay hain"
  50,18,koi baat is ki zabaan par nahi aati magar aik nigehbaan is ke paas tayyar rehta hai
  50,19,aur mout ki be hoshi haqeeqat kholnay ko taari hogayi. ( ae ensaan ) yahi ( woh haalat ) hai jis se to bhagta tha
  50,20,aur sor phonka jaye ga. yahi ( azaab ke ) vayd ka din hai
  50,21,aur har shakhs ( hamaray samnay ) aeye ga. aik ( farishta ) is ke sath chalanay wala hoga aur aik ( is ke amlon ki ) gawahi dainay wala
  50,22,( yeh woh din hai ke ) is se to ghaafil ho raha tha. ab hum ne tujh par se parda uttha diya. to aaj teri nigah taiz hai
  50,23,aur is ka hum nasheen ( farishta ) kahe ga ke yeh ( aamaal nama ) mere paas haazir hai
  50,24,( hukum hoga ke ) har sarkash nashukray ko dozakh mein daal do
  50,25,jo maal mein bukhal karne wala hadd se bherne wala shubhay nikaalte wala tha
  50,26,jis ne khuda ke sath aur mabood muqarrar kar rakhay they. to is ko sakht azaab mein daal do
  50,27,is ka saathi ( shetan ) kahe ga ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar mein ne is ko gumraah nahikiya tha balkay yeh aap hi raste se daur bhatka howa tha
  50,28,( khuda ) farmaiye ga ke hamaray huzoor mein radukad nah karo. hum tumahray paas pehlay hi ( azaab ki ) vayd bhaij chuke they
  50,29,hamaray haan baat badla nahi karti aur hum bundon par zulm nahikiya karte
  50,30,is din hum dozakh se poucheen ge kekiya to bhar gayi? woh kahe gi ke kuch aur bhi hai ?
  50,31,aur bahisht parhaiz garon ke qareeb kar di jaye gi ( ke mutlaq ) daur nah hogi
  50,32,yahi woh cheez hai jis ka tum se wadakiya jata tha ( yani ) har rujoo laane walay hifazat karne walay se
  50,33,jo khuda se ban dekhe darta hai aur rujoo laane wala dil le kar aaya
  50,34,is mein salamti ke sath daakhil hojao. yeh hamesha rehne ka din hai
  50,35,wahan woh jo chahain ge un ke liye haazir hai aur hamaray haan aur bhi ( bohat kuch ) hai
  50,36,aur hum ne un se pehlay kayi ummatain halaak kar dalain. woh un se qowat mein kahin barh kar they woh shehron mein gasht karne lagey.kiya kahin bhagnay ki jagah hai ?
  50,37,jo shakhs dil ( aagah ) rakhta hai ya dil se mutwajjah ho kar santa hai is ke liye is mein nasiyaat hai
  50,38,aur hum ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo ( makhloqaat ) un mein hai sab ko chay din mein bana diya. aur hum ko zara takan nahi hui
  50,39,to jo kuch yeh ( kufar ) bektay hain is par sabr karo aur aftaab ke tulu honay se pehlay aur is ke ghuroob honay se pehlay apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karte raho
  50,40,aur raat ke baaz auqaat mein bhi aur namaz ke baad bhi is ( ke naam ) ki tasbeeh kiya karo
  50,41,aur suno jis din pukarnay wala nazdeek ki jagah se pukare ga
  50,42,jis din log cheekh yaqeenan sun len ge. wohi nikal parney ka din hai
  50,43,hum hi to zindah karte hain aur hum hi maartay hain aur hamaray hi paas lout kar aana hai
  50,44,is din zameen un par se phatt jaye gi aur woh jhat patt nikal kharray hon ge. yeh jama karna hamein aasaan hai
  50,45,yeh log jo kuch kehte hain hamein khoob maloom hai aur tum un par zabardasti karne walay nahi ho. pas jo hamaray ( azaab ki ) vayd se daray is ko quran se nasiyaat karte raho
